<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy 23rd Birthday 🎂</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body{
margin:0;
font-family:Poppins;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffe0f0,#fff3d6);
text-align:center;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

.card{
max-width:750px;
margin:40px auto;
background:white;
padding:25px;
border-radius:20px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

h1{color:#ff4d88}

button{
padding:12px 20px;
border:none;
border-radius:30px;
background:#ff4d88;
color:white;
font-size:16px;
cursor:pointer;
margin-top:15px;
}

.hidden{display:none}

#gift{
margin-top:20px;
background:#fff0f6;
padding:15px;
border-radius:15px;
}

.confetti{
position:fixed;
width:8px;
height:8px;
top:-10px;
animation:fall linear forwards;
z-index:999;
}

@keyframes fall{
to{transform:translateY(110vh) rotate(720deg);}
}

.small{font-size:13px;color:gray}

.bar{
height:10px;
background:#eee;
border-radius:20px;
overflow:hidden;
margin:15px 0;
}

.progress{
height:100%;
width:0%;
background:#ff4d88;
transition:0.4s;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<audio id="music" loop>
<source src="https://www.soundhelix.com/examples/mp3/SoundHelix-Song-1.mp3">
</audio>

<div class="card">

<h1>🎂 DENDITO OS UPDATE</h1>

<p><b>Dendito Ahza Ghulammahdi</b></p>

<p>System menemukan update baru tersedia.</p>

<p class="small">🐱 meow mode: activated</p>

<button onclick="start()">INSTALL UPDATE</button>

<div id="gift" class="hidden">

<h2>🎉 HAPPY 23RD BIRTHDAY 🎉</h2>

<p>
Selamat ulang tahun 🐱<br>
Semoga kamu makin kuat, bahagia, dan semua urusan dipermudah.
</p>

<hr>

<h3>🎁 HADIAH</h3>

<p>✨ +100 Kebahagiaan</p>
<p>🍀 +100 Keberuntungan</p>
<p>💪 +100 Kesehatan</p>
<p>💸 +100 Rezeki</p>

<hr>

<h3>👑 BONUS ITEM</h3>

<p><b>Kurcaci Cantik</b></p>

<p>
Status: Langka ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐<br>
Tinggi: Rahasia Negara<br>
Skill: Bikin senyum tiba-tiba
</p>

<p class="small">
“tidak bisa dikembalikan, tapi efek bahagianya permanen”
</p>

<br>

<h3>🐱 SYSTEM MESSAGE</h3>

<p>Update: SUCCESS</p>
<p>Doa terkirim ke semesta ✨</p>

<h3>🌱 Welcome to Chapter 23</h3>

<p><b>Regards, Kurcaci Cantik 🤍</b></p>

</div>

</div>

<script>
function start(){

document.getElementById("music").play().catch(()=>{});

document.getElementById("gift").classList.remove("hidden");

for(let i=0;i<100;i++){
let d=document.createElement("div");
d.classList.add("confetti");
d.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
d.style.background="hsl("+Math.random()*360+",100%,60%)";
d.style.animationDuration=(Math.random()*3+2)+"s";
document.body.appendChild(d);

setTimeout(()=>d.remove(),5000);
}

}
</script>

</body>
</html>
